		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="438" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水飘浮灵喷出1个弱追踪性的水弹，移动速度较慢，造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/水飘浮灵.assets/Image_26.png')" x="1268" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/水飘浮灵.assets/Image_27.png')" x="1248" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水飘浮灵旋转，在玩家处产生水喷，造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害，处于该范围的任意原魔会</span><span color="#99ffff">恢复40%生命值</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="223" width="419" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfccff">(满怒施放)<span color="#ffffff">水飘浮灵拉长身子，挤压产生水爆，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="436" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水飘浮灵死亡。<br/><span color="#9fccff">未满怒：</span><span>直接爆炸，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害；<br/></span><span color="#9fccff">满怒：</span><span>蓄力爆炸，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">120%</span><span>伤害，若周围20m内存在其他飘浮灵，则产生对应数量的水泡，</span><span color="#99ffff">恢复其20%生命值</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
